333
00:31:28,066 --> 00:31:29,151
<i>Trancado.</i>

334
00:31:39,369 --> 00:31:40,412
<i>Vamos.</i>

335
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:12,444
<i>Ativar botas e luvas de gravidade.</i>

336
00:32:20,619 --> 00:32:22,246
<i>Nebula, vá.</i>

337
00:32:57,739 --> 00:32:59,783
